38, \"to\": 7445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, since it was those awful \\\"conservatives\\\" who were saying this, the online lefty coterie has to line up like trained seals to deride, gaslight, and gleefully mock us hillbillies.But why would this coterie of online lefty Catholics believe Jolly if he said his crucifixion was merely a pagan scarecrow?\", \"from\": 7469, \"to\": 7774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7694, \"end\": 7703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999996470662095, \"rank\": 3.1225304095627015e-07, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 7758, \"end\": 7763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\", \"score\": 0.999990626063375, \"rank\": 3.9112725195013496e-06, \"text\": \"pagan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those awful \\\"conservatives\", \"from\": 7487, \"to\": 7513}, {\"ngram\": \"the online lefty coterie\", \"from\": 7537, \"to\": 7561}, {\"ngram\": \"trained seals\", \"from\": 7582, \"to\": 7595}, {\"ngram\": \"gaslight\", \"from\": 7607, \"to\": 7615}, {\"ngram\": \"us hillbillies\", \"from\": 7636, \"to\": 7650}, {\"ngram\": \"this coterie\", \"from\": 7665, \"to\": 7677}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 7712, \"to\": 7717}, {\"ngram\": \"his crucifixion\", \"from\": 7729, \"to\": 7744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And why would they line up to mock any criticism of his Olympic Last Supper?\", \"from\": 7775, \"to\": 7851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any criticism\", \"from\": 7810, \"to\": 7823}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic Last Supper\", \"from\": 7827, \"to\": 7850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Besides a whole lot of gaslighting going on, this group hates anything that smacks of that great evil: \\\"conservatism.\", \"from\": 7