19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the blasphemy\", \"from\": 21930, \"to\": 21943}, {\"ngram\": \"a nonresponse\", \"from\": 21948, \"to\": 21961}, {\"ngram\": \"the blasphemy\", \"from\": 21965, \"to\": 21978}, {\"ngram\": \"a condemnation\", \"from\": 21990, \"to\": 22004}, {\"ngram\": \"war\", \"from\": 22008, \"to\": 22011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Go Francis!\", \"from\": 22013, \"to\": 22025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22017, \"end\": 22024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 0.9280218828923935, \"rank\": 0.07703740188964303, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He hates those nasty culture warriors, just like we do!\", \"from\": 22026, \"to\": 22081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those nasty culture warriors\", \"from\": 22035, \"to\": 22063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That this was an image of the Last Supper is clear to all who can see beyond their ideological lens.\", \"from\": 22081, \"to\": 22182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an image\", \"from\": 22096, \"to\": 22104}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 22108, \"to\": 22123}, {\"ngram\": \"their ideological lens\", \"from\": 22159, \"to\": 22181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That Last Supper moment was almost perfectly framed and was a perfect stick in the eye of the Catholic Faith.\", \"from\": 22183, \"to\": 22292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22277, \"end\": 22285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999995371749654, \"rank\": 1.9576860043678608e-07, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That Last Supper moment\", \"from\": 22183, \"to\": 22206}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfect stick\", \"from\": 22243, \"to\": 22258}, {\"ngram\": \"the eye\", \"from\": 22262, \"to\": 22269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, since it was those awful \\\"conservatives\\\" who were saying this, the online lefty coterie has to line up like trained seals to deride, gaslight, and gleefully mock us hillbillies.But why would this coterie of online lefty Catholics believe Jolly if he said his crucifixion was merely a pagan scarecrow?\", \"from\": 22293, \"to\": 22598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22518, \"end\": 22527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.999998901876359, \"rank\": 6.924403415511039e-07, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 22582, \"end\": 22587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\", \"score\": 0.9999818350562714, \"rank\": 6.587256056109059e-06, \"text\": \"pagan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those awful \\\"conservatives\", \"from\": 22311, \"to\": 22337}, {\"ngram\": \"the online lefty coterie\", \"from\": 22361, \"to\": 22385}, {\"ngram\": \"trained seals\", \"from\": 22406, \"to\": 22419}, {\"ngram\": \"gaslight\", \"from\": 22431, \"to\": 22439}, {\"ngram\": \"us hillbillies\", \"from\": 22460, \"to\": 22474}, {\"ngram\": \"this coterie\", \"from\": 22489, \"to\": 22501}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 22536, \"to\": 22541}, {\"ngram\": \"his crucifixion\", \"from\": 22553, \"to\": 22568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And why would they line up to mock any criticism of his Olympic Last Supper?\", \"from\": 22599, \"to\": 22675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any criticism\", \"from\": 22634, \"to\": 22647}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic Last Supper\", \"from\": 22651, \"to\": 22674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Besides a whole lot of gaslighting going on, this group hates anything that smacks of that great evil: \\\"conservatism.\", \"from\": 22676, \"to\": 22793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a whole lot\", \"from\": 22684, \"to\": 22695}, {\"ngram\": \"this group\", \"from\": 22721, \"to\": 22731}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 22738, \"to\": 22746}, {\"ngram\": \"that great evil\", \"from\": 22762, \"to\": 22777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the \\\"conservatives\\\" do something, even something terrific, these folks hate it.\", \"from\": 22793, \"to\": 22876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\\"conservatives\", \"from\": 22797, \"to\": 22815}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 22820, \"to\": 22829}, {\"ngram\": \"these folks\", \"from\": 22856, \"to\": 22867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If \\\"conservatives\\\" criticize something, even something awful, these folks defend it.\", \"from\": 22877, \"to\": 22961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"conservatives\", \"from\": 22881, \"to\": 22894}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 22906, \"to\": 22915}, {\"ngram\": \"even something\", \"from\": 22917, \"to\": 22931}, {\"ngram\": \"these folks\", \"from\": 22939, \"to\": 22950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why?\", \"from\": 22962, \"to\": 22966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it is because \\\"conservatives\\\" hurt their feelings or their sensibilities or something way back at Steubenville or Christendom or someplace where they bumped up against such \\\"conservatives.\", \"from\": 22967, \"to\": 23163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23073, \"end\": 23085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Franciscan_University_of_Steubenville\", \"score\": 0.9985985611821716, \"rank\": 0.0010205250937795232, \"text\": \"Steubenville\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Franciscan_University_of_Steubenville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Franciscan_University_of_Steubenville\"}, {\"begin\": 23089, \"end\": 23100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9438093541989602, \"rank\": 0.059509186471297645, \"text\": \"Christendom\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"conservatives\", \"from\": 22990, \"to\": 23003}, {\"ngram\": \"their feelings\", \"from\": 23010, \"to\": 23024}, {\"ngram\": \"their sensibilities\", \"from\": 23028, \"to\": 23047}, {\"ngram\": \"such \\\"conservatives\", \"from\": 23143, \"to\": 23162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Consider the National Eucharistic Congress.\", \"from\": 23163, \"to\": 23207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23186, \"end\": 23206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\", \"score\": 0.9999738869505611, \"rank\": 2.611373129558213e-05, \"text\": \"Eucharistic Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This coterie of new lefties really hated it!\", \"from\": 23208, \"to\": 23252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This coterie\", \"from\": 23208, \"to\": 23220}, {\"ngram\": \"new lefties\", \"from\": 23224, \"to\": 23235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, they hated it with the possible exception of the part where Gloria Purvis scolded us once again about \\\"racism.\\\"\", \"from\": 23253, \"to\": 23370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23319, \"end\": 23332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gloria_Purvis\", \"score\": 0.99999722461358, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gloria Purvis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"ht